WEBVTT

00:00:06.405 --> 00:00:12.565
Sahaj Bhajan - [Ma hum par kripa karna
- From 00:07 to 00:22]

00:00:22.435 --> 00:00:29.645
Sahaj Bhajan - [Isliye Mataji humko darshan
hue tumhare - From 00:22 to 00:30]

00:00:29.645 --> 00:00:39.403
Jai, jai [Shri Mataji arrives]

00:00:41.425 --> 00:00:52.955
Sahaj Bhajan - [Sarva mangal mangalye - Vishwa
Vandita Nirmala Mata - From 00:41 to 09:30]

00:09:32.743 --> 00:09:38.133
About 200? Yogi, hurry up, everyone
is standing.

00:09:38.133 --> 00:09:42.214
I told them to bring them here
somehow or make a way here.

00:09:42.625 --> 00:09:51.605
There are a lot of people inside.
Can see it from here. Did you tell them?

00:09:53.287 --> 00:09:59.497
Look, those people who can't get in,
make room; let these people in.

00:09:59.497 --> 00:10:05.656
Sahaja Yogi: I request all the brothers
who are standing on the side, there is
plenty of space here, please come.

00:10:06.012 --> 00:10:10.662
There's room inside, please come and sit.
There's plenty of room on the side.

00:10:12.102 --> 00:10:15.113
It will be great if everyone sits down.

00:10:26.555 --> 00:10:37.335
Shri Mataji, all of us (UNCLEAR) from Delhi,
who have gathered here, extends Her
heartfelt greetings to you.

00:11:09.102 --> 00:11:13.082
Shri Mataji: [Aside - It's hot right now,
I'm sweating, later.]

00:11:26.988 --> 00:11:32.328
[MARATHI]

00:13:12.259 --> 00:13:19.539
I bow to all the seekers of Truth.

00:13:24.027 --> 00:13:31.457
I have been told to speak in English
initially and then switch to Hindi.

00:13:31.994 --> 00:13:37.654
You are, you accept all this, right?

00:13:45.659 --> 00:13:49.259
I bow to all the seekers of Truth.

00:13:51.356 --> 00:13:59.746
At the very outset we have to know
what is the Truth and what are we
seeking.

00:14:00.936 --> 00:14:05.826
Why this seeking has started in these
recent years?

00:14:10.796 --> 00:14:18.316
We have Science, by which we have
overgrown outwardly.

00:14:19.703 --> 00:14:26.003
We have different devices by which our
life has become more comfortable,
maybe.

00:14:29.261 --> 00:14:32.951
But Science cannot answer many
questions

00:14:33.453 --> 00:14:39.193
and one of the questions it cannot
answer is, 'Why are we here on this
Earth?'

00:14:41.349 --> 00:14:43.979
Also Science is amoral.

00:14:44.702 --> 00:14:55.950
It does not give you any line of action
that will benefit you and that will
nourish you.

00:15:00.099 --> 00:15:03.469
Of course there is nothing against
Science as such

00:15:03.484 --> 00:15:09.674
but it is very incomplete and takes
people into imbalances.

00:15:11.275 --> 00:15:17.305
There are so many defects which I'm
not going to describe today but

00:15:17.305 --> 00:15:22.410
main thing is that it does not give
you the idea of reality,

00:15:24.265 --> 00:15:36.235
it does not give you the totality; also, it
does not give you any ascent in your
spiritual life.

00:15:40.306 --> 00:15:48.426
So much in the West - also in India -
not to that extent but yes, quite a lot,

00:15:48.426 --> 00:15:51.751
we have progressed in Science in
every way.

00:15:55.770 --> 00:16:02.050
But what do we find. There's a decline
in the character of human-beings,

00:16:02.722 --> 00:16:09.252
in the society the families are breaking,
children are going astray.

00:16:09.335 --> 00:16:15.295
Everywhere we find there's such a
decline in the quality of life

00:16:15.367 --> 00:16:22.547
and sometimes we cannot also say that
these things are done even by human-
beings.

00:16:22.598 --> 00:16:31.428
Impossible to explain why people have
fallen to such a low level of existence

00:16:31.428 --> 00:16:37.137
and think that that is the best life.
They have lost all the capacity to feel

00:16:37.137 --> 00:16:43.471
that we are going very fast towards
our complete destruction.

00:16:44.940 --> 00:16:49.030
In the West, I think, the destruction is
working out from within

00:16:49.815 --> 00:16:56.595
and this destruction is not even felt. On
the contrary people think

00:16:56.595 --> 00:17:05.873
they're martyrs, if they are getting
destroyed. So, the seeking has started.

00:17:06.858 --> 00:17:12.978
The human beings are now faced with
the problem as to, "Why are we on this
Earth?"

00:17:12.982 --> 00:17:21.452
"Are we here just to get into this rut
of this rat race?"

00:17:21.669 --> 00:17:26.589
"Or as we here just to insure our lives
and ultimately die?"

00:17:26.715 --> 00:17:30.945
"Is that the aim of our life, is that
the value of our life?"

00:17:32.201 --> 00:17:41.971
In the West, I must say, there have been
very few talks about the inner life,

00:17:42.191 --> 00:17:50.681
about the inner self, and even in India
there has been so much of work done

00:17:51.205 --> 00:17:57.485
but, after the British when they went
away, we suddenly took also -

00:17:57.485 --> 00:18:00.566
specially our intellectuals have become
very Westernized.

00:18:00.937 --> 00:18:07.727
They cannot think that India had
anything sensible within, that they
could talk about.

00:18:07.727 --> 00:18:16.752
About anybody they write left and right
and try to spread in a way

00:18:16.901 --> 00:18:21.111
that Western ideas of modernism.

00:18:22.500 --> 00:18:29.490
This modernism, if it had brought
any kind of good results, one would
have accepted.

00:18:29.490 --> 00:18:33.939
Sitting down here in India we don't
know what they are up to,

00:18:33.939 --> 00:18:38.225
in what conditions they are,
how terribly disturbed they are

00:18:38.225 --> 00:18:41.407
what problems they are facing -
we have no idea.

00:18:41.407 --> 00:18:44.171
We have only one problem - is
our poverty.

00:18:45.895 --> 00:18:52.455
Also, when we start copying them, we'll
have the same problems coming into
India.

00:18:54.536 --> 00:19:00.756
So it is important that also the West
must understand that they must

00:19:00.756 --> 00:19:06.511
see that this great tree they have
produced of modern civilization,

00:19:06.511 --> 00:19:10.262
must have its roots somewhere,
and where are those roots?

00:19:10.262 --> 00:19:14.561
And without the nourishment from the
roots, how are they going to prosper,

00:19:14.561 --> 00:19:20.353
how are they going to live, how are they
going to exist, how are they going to
enjoy their life?

00:19:22.048 --> 00:19:27.118
The roots are in this country.
This is a great country of yoga.

00:19:30.223 --> 00:19:36.853
Is vibrated with the All-Pervading
Power of Divine Love.

00:19:37.773 --> 00:19:45.259
Though we Indians are not yet aware,
that to be born in this country itself
is a great boon.

00:19:45.857 --> 00:19:51.807
Neither they are aware as to what, what
has been done by the great saints in
this country

00:19:52.749 --> 00:19:54.789
and how much they have worked hard,

00:19:54.789 --> 00:20:02.920
that one day this country should
spread spirituality all over the world.

00:20:02.939 --> 00:20:10.449
Without that you are still not complete.

00:20:11.813 --> 00:20:16.353
We are human-beings, we have
reached the state of human awareness

00:20:16.366 --> 00:20:24.436
but we do not know what is Absolute
Truth - we are living very, very relatively.

00:20:24.519 --> 00:20:27.399
Some people think this kind of
government is good,

00:20:27.399 --> 00:20:30.233
somebody thinks that kind of
government is good, somebody thinks

00:20:30.233 --> 00:20:33.088
that Economics should be like that,
another thinks like that.

00:20:33.088 --> 00:20:37.283
And there's all the times discussions,
arguments and fighting going on.

00:20:37.283 --> 00:20:39.352
Ultimately we end up in wars.

00:20:42.528 --> 00:20:51.228
This relative life that we have, doesn't
give us any clear-cut idea as to what
is the Absolute.

00:20:52.974 --> 00:21:00.104
Unless and until we find that
Absoluteness, we cannot understand
the Truth.

00:21:00.158 --> 00:21:06.258
So those who are seeking Truth, have to
strive to know the Absolute.

00:21:08.110 --> 00:21:16.380
At this human awareness the problem
is, that we are either involved with our
body, mind,

00:21:16.930 --> 00:21:29.350
also so-called spirituality, emotions -
all these are just appendages, you can
say,

00:21:30.147 --> 00:21:40.077
appendages for your being. We say this
is my body, this is my body, this is my
mind, this is my mind,

00:21:40.077 --> 00:21:45.545
this is my emotions, this is my house,
this is my wife - who is this my?

00:21:45.545 --> 00:21:53.805
Who is the one who owns it? The one
who owns it is the Spirit.

00:21:55.171 --> 00:22:02.351
Is the Spirit in your heart, the Spirit
which has not yet come into your
attention.

00:22:02.351 --> 00:22:08.025
The light of the Spirit it has not yet
come into your attention, that's why
you think,

00:22:08.025 --> 00:22:13.811
you are this body, you are this mind.
You are not. You are the Pure Spirit.

00:22:15.244 --> 00:22:23.154
You are, whether you know it or not.
Also there's another thing one has to
know,

00:22:24.555 --> 00:22:31.105
that there is a All-Pervading Power of
Divine Love, which does all this

00:22:31.105 --> 00:22:42.351
living work of producing these beautiful
flowers, running our heart, looking after
our digestion.

00:22:43.194 --> 00:22:53.474
Every sort of a living work is done by
this All-Pervading Power of Divine Love.

00:22:53.474 --> 00:22:57.698
In Sanskrit we call it Brahmchaitanya.
Whatever you may call it.

00:22:57.698 --> 00:23:02.675
In the Bible it is called as the Cool
Breeze of the Holy Ghost -

00:23:05.100 --> 00:23:10.630
is the power of the Holy Ghost. Also in
Koran it is called as Ruh.

00:23:11.615 --> 00:23:19.045
In the religions where they have talked
about the nirakar, about formless,

00:23:19.045 --> 00:23:26.362
they have talked about it. So, this All-
Pervading Power of Paramchaitanya

00:23:26.362 --> 00:23:35.274
exists and we have to get united with
that, that is the real yoga.

00:23:35.807 --> 00:23:40.627
Standing on your head and doing
acrobats, is not yoga.

00:23:40.853 --> 00:23:45.733
Or reading books and doing mental
acrobats is also not yoga.

00:23:47.214 --> 00:23:56.884
What is important is that you have to
grow above your mental capacity.

00:23:56.884 --> 00:24:02.567
All the Western world is full of mental
projections

00:24:02.567 --> 00:24:06.882
and these mental projections are linear
in their nature.

00:24:07.987 --> 00:24:19.087
They go up to a point, but they are not
substantiated by Truth so they decline
and they fall.

00:24:19.087 --> 00:24:26.952
So we have now decline in all our
standards. Then now we cannot have

00:24:26.952 --> 00:24:34.101
people like Mozart, Bach, Strauss
- we cannot have.

00:24:34.258 --> 00:24:47.848
We cannot have people like Leonardo
da Vinci or anyone of those great
artist

00:24:48.628 --> 00:24:57.758
because we have lost our capacity
even as a human-being and we are

00:24:57.758 --> 00:25:04.566
trying to do something which has no
even the power of humanity.

00:25:05.655 --> 00:25:11.265
Thus this decline is so obvious and
evident in every walk of life,

00:25:11.265 --> 00:25:16.254
everywhere you see, even in India you'll
see that very much so.

00:25:16.947 --> 00:25:23.717
We cannot blame anybody for that,
because so far, we have not found the
Absolute Truth.

00:25:23.838 --> 00:25:27.248
Unless and until we have found out the
Absolute Truth,

00:25:27.248 --> 00:25:34.539
how can we know what is the right
thing to do. Now whatever I'm telling you,

00:25:34.539 --> 00:25:39.110
you need not believe Me because blind
faith has never helped us.

00:25:39.239 --> 00:25:45.009
But whatever I'm telling you, you can
take it as a hypothesis and if it works,

00:25:45.474 --> 00:25:51.444
then you have to accept as Divine
Laws. And if it works in such a way,

00:25:51.444 --> 00:25:56.113
that you obviously see it working, that
you can work it out,

00:25:56.113 --> 00:25:59.015
then of course, you should not deny it.

00:26:03.320 --> 00:26:08.970
I think, there are many people who
are talking about it all over the world.

00:26:09.000 --> 00:26:13.890
Except in India the intellectuals have
become really, I don't know, deaf and
dumb.

00:26:13.890 --> 00:26:18.870
But otherwise, in other countries I've
seen everywhere, you'll find, at least,

00:26:18.870 --> 00:26:24.143
3 to 4 people who are genuinely
interested in knowing the Absolute
Truth.

00:26:24.822 --> 00:26:29.732
Especially Russia and the Eastern Bloc
people I was amazed to see

00:26:29.732 --> 00:26:34.175
how they are so much interested to
know what is the Truth is.

00:26:34.175 --> 00:26:38.300
They had never known God, they have
never known Divine, they have never known

00:26:38.300 --> 00:26:41.774
anything about it - Kundalini, of course,
is very far away from them.

00:26:41.774 --> 00:26:46.606
But the way they took to Sahaja Yoga,
it surprises Me.

00:26:46.926 --> 00:26:52.566
In some villages we have about thirty
thousand Sahaja Yogis.

00:26:53.663 --> 00:26:58.843
It's very remarkable how these people
didn't take to materialism so much,

00:26:58.843 --> 00:27:03.569
as they have taken in the West and
they know very well now,

00:27:03.569 --> 00:27:06.660
that matter doesn't give you joy, it
doesn't give you happiness,

00:27:06.660 --> 00:27:10.488
it doesn't give you fulfilment. There's
something beyond this matter,

00:27:10.488 --> 00:27:17.662
beyond this mind that we have to
achieve. And that is what is Sahaja
Yoga.

00:27:19.036 --> 00:27:27.136
Sahaja Yoga is where 'Saha' means with
and 'ja' is born, with you is born,

00:27:28.027 --> 00:27:37.417
the right, the fundamental right you
have, to achieve this yoga, means, the
union with the Divine.

00:27:37.719 --> 00:27:42.299
All the saints of this country have
spoken about it, while even

00:27:42.299 --> 00:27:46.527
many people in England, as you know,
that there have been William Blake,

00:27:46.527 --> 00:27:51.823
now if you read William Blake, English
used to think he was a mad poet -
he's not.

00:27:52.261 --> 00:27:58.931
He was the seer and he talked about
it. In every country you'll find somebody

00:27:58.964 --> 00:28:08.354
who has been speaking about this
higher life and these inner value
systems.

00:28:10.211 --> 00:28:17.271
For Sahaja Yoga you don't have to
argue, think or put in any effort.

00:28:17.271 --> 00:28:25.240
Nowadays I've found that the Buddhism
is very popular in, in the West,

00:28:25.705 --> 00:28:30.205
because it appeals to their brains, it
goes into their brains

00:28:30.205 --> 00:28:33.096
and they can think about it and argue
about it.

00:28:33.952 --> 00:28:38.342
Nothing wrong with Buddhism but
as far as Buddha is concerned,

00:28:38.342 --> 00:28:45.889
he was all right. That was the time when
he had to do this tapasya, as you call it,

00:28:46.150 --> 00:28:53.940
the whole penance, but these times are
over. At that time even Christ had to do
also

00:28:53.940 --> 00:29:01.509
and at that time Mahavira also had to
do. Those were the times but today's
times are different.

00:29:01.509 --> 00:29:05.541
These are special times, I call them
Blossom Times.

00:29:05.541 --> 00:29:10.796
And this is the time where many
flowers have come up.

00:29:10.796 --> 00:29:15.788
These are seekers of ancient times -
were seeking the Truth

00:29:15.788 --> 00:29:20.835
and today in this modern times, which
we call as Kaliyuga, they are born

00:29:21.428 --> 00:29:28.828
to get the reward of their seeking. They
maybe Indians, they maybe Germans,

00:29:28.828 --> 00:29:34.085
they maybe English, they maybe
anyone, they have to get this reward

00:29:34.085 --> 00:29:38.077
for their seeking what they have been
doing and the time has come today.

00:29:38.137 --> 00:29:42.887
When I say that, people think I'm being
very assertive, but it's a fact.

00:29:43.985 --> 00:29:50.435
The truth is, that today is the time for
them to get the reward of their seeking.

00:29:51.795 --> 00:29:58.115
They have already told you about the
Kundalini and the inner mechanism.

00:29:58.984 --> 00:30:06.404
Even to know about that, is just mental.
Even to listen to My lecture is also
mental.

00:30:07.041 --> 00:30:16.031
You have to go beyond your mind, so,
then, something has to happen.

00:30:16.229 --> 00:30:20.949
And that happening is nothing but the
awakening of the Kundalini,

00:30:21.916 --> 00:30:29.216
which is really the Pure Desire in your
mind because with other desires you
never feel satisfied.

00:30:29.904 --> 00:30:33.964
Unless and until you become the Spirit
you'll never be satisfied,

00:30:33.964 --> 00:30:38.216
you'll never be happy, specially the
ones who are seekers today.

00:30:38.216 --> 00:30:43.863
Of course there are many who are
seeking in money, materialism or
maybe in power.

00:30:45.177 --> 00:30:49.597
But they are not satisfied people. They
have not achieved anything,

00:30:49.597 --> 00:30:53.089
they don't know the goal of their life;
they are just moving with the winds

00:30:53.089 --> 00:30:59.676
the way wind moves them. So to get
to understand what is the purpose

00:31:00.227 --> 00:31:09.057
of your being a Spirit is that - this is in
a very simple manner I'm saying -

00:31:09.057 --> 00:31:17.356
that you enter into the Kingdom of God.
Is not the kingdom of America or

00:31:17.356 --> 00:31:24.614
kingdom of India or anything like that,
but is the Kingdom of God.

00:31:25.886 --> 00:31:37.286
It's all for your well-being and as I said,
as seekers you are all respected, and
you all have to get it.

00:31:37.969 --> 00:31:42.929
The problems with us are many but I
can put them in two category -

00:31:42.929 --> 00:31:46.802
is one, is our ego and a another one
conditioning.

00:31:47.390 --> 00:31:55.460
These two things bind our life. We live
in the past and the future but

00:31:55.460 --> 00:32:01.042
we cannot stand in the present. But
when this happening takes place,

00:32:01.691 --> 00:32:06.971
then, you're surprised, that the
thoughts that were coming

00:32:06.971 --> 00:32:11.714
from the past and future just stop,
and you are thoughtlessly aware.

00:32:11.913 --> 00:32:19.073
This is the first situation, first stage, first
state, where you are thoughtlessly
aware.

00:32:20.867 --> 00:32:27.117
This lasts for a short time that's why
Patanjali had called as 'savichar',

00:32:27.117 --> 00:32:33.751
means with thought - awareness with
thought. But in Sahaja yoga, I've seen,

00:32:33.751 --> 00:32:40.492
this can be achieved very easily
through certain time you give to your
meditation

00:32:41.158 --> 00:32:46.578
and only in the present, which is the
reality, you grow and thus you grow

00:32:46.578 --> 00:32:55.283
and grow and reach a state, which we
call as, doubtless awareness,

00:32:55.283 --> 00:33:01.603
which means - also in Sanskrit is called
as 'Nirvikalpa samadhi'.

00:33:01.793 --> 00:33:05.715
This is a state which has to be
achieved in Sahaja Yoga.

00:33:06.272 --> 00:33:09.642
Now some people want to know,
"We want to have God's realization."

00:33:09.642 --> 00:33:13.780
I mean all funny ideas. So many books
are there, then they read them

00:33:13.780 --> 00:33:16.782
and then come, "Mother, we want God's
realization." Means what?

00:33:16.782 --> 00:33:21.185
What does it mean 'God's realization?'
They [UNCLEAR - Challenge?] Me.

00:33:24.249 --> 00:33:30.069
But what happens that your Central
Nervous System itself gets enlightened

00:33:30.069 --> 00:33:37.497
by this happening and the light of the
Spirit is felt by your Central Nervous
System.

00:33:37.497 --> 00:33:46.553
As in our evolution we have so many
other capacities compared to animals,

00:33:47.475 --> 00:33:51.135
that are all felt on our Central Nervous
System.

00:33:51.276 --> 00:33:56.936
In the same way our Central Nervous
System itself gets enlightened,

00:33:56.936 --> 00:34:03.424
which is in Sanskrit language is used as
'Vid' from where the word Ved has
come.

00:34:03.424 --> 00:34:09.492
'Vid' is to feel on your Central Nervous
System. Another is 'Bodh'.

00:34:09.492 --> 00:34:16.504
Bodh is to feel on your Central Nervous
System. These things you can easily
feel.

00:34:17.711 --> 00:34:22.641
On your Central Nervous System your
fingers get enlightened

00:34:22.641 --> 00:34:34.847
and you start feeling on your fingertips
the All-Pervading Power of Divine Love.

00:34:34.847 --> 00:34:41.721
You can feel it like cool breeze on your
fingertips. They get enlightened.

00:34:41.721 --> 00:34:49.255
For the first time you feel there is a
power around you. Then when you grow

00:34:49.427 --> 00:34:58.587
as I said, you start becoming
collectively conscious, collectively
conscious.

00:34:59.160 --> 00:35:03.635
Not that you get Self-knowledge, that
you know about your own centres,

00:35:03.635 --> 00:35:12.415
but you become collectively conscious,
meaning, that you can feel others, their
centres.

00:35:12.988 --> 00:35:18.838
Though all our problems in this world
are from human-beings, most of them.

00:35:20.380 --> 00:35:27.150
They all come from these centres. And
if these centres, are being somehow,

00:35:27.150 --> 00:35:34.386
are cured, then we are alright and if we
can help others to cure their centres,

00:35:35.836 --> 00:35:43.766
what will happen - a new race of
enlightened people will be established.

00:35:44.683 --> 00:35:51.643
This is the time of Last Judgment. This
is the time of Last Judgment where
people

00:35:51.643 --> 00:35:55.600
have to judge themselves. If they want
to go to Hell, it's quite easy

00:35:55.660 --> 00:36:01.260
and if they want to go to Heaven, that's
also quite easy but the choice is yours.

00:36:01.292 --> 00:36:05.312
Nobody can force a human-being to
choose.

00:36:05.374 --> 00:36:13.744
That's his freedom, that's her freedom,
because freedom has been granted

00:36:13.982 --> 00:36:22.862
and cannot be taken away. So now, for
you it is important to decide today,

00:36:22.862 --> 00:36:29.849
tonight, whether you want to have your
Self-realization or not.

00:36:29.849 --> 00:36:34.052
I cannot force on you, I cannot.
I respect your freedom.

00:36:34.052 --> 00:36:39.165
I cannot force it, so you have to
decide. But remember,

00:36:39.165 --> 00:36:44.872
that you are a human-being and you
are at the epitome of evolution.

00:36:44.872 --> 00:36:48.957
You are the glorious ones. Your glory
you don't know.

00:36:48.957 --> 00:36:51.125
You don't know how many
powers you have.

00:36:51.125 --> 00:36:55.147
Unless and until you get your
realization, you will not know.

00:36:55.147 --> 00:36:59.009
For example, this instrument, if it is not
connected to the mains,

00:36:59.009 --> 00:37:03.231
it has no identity, it has no meaning, it
has no use. In the same way,

00:37:03.451 --> 00:37:11.891
your situation is, and once you get this
realization, then absolutely,

00:37:11.891 --> 00:37:16.601
it's a different world into which you will
be. I'm telling you we have here,

00:37:16.601 --> 00:37:20.918
I don't know, they say there are people
from sixty nations, but whatever it is

00:37:20.918 --> 00:37:27.547
if you see them, you'll be very happy -
everybody describes them as angels.

00:37:27.547 --> 00:37:33.013
They don't fight, they don't quarrel,
there's no argument, nothing.

00:37:33.204 --> 00:37:39.694
They enjoy each other, they love each
other. Apart from that, of course,

00:37:39.694 --> 00:37:44.903
they are enjoying each other by also,
they pull each other's legs,

00:37:44.903 --> 00:37:48.804
that I know and sometimes make fun,
but that's how they live.

00:37:48.804 --> 00:37:53.665
There is no malice, there's no hatred,
there's no jealousy, nothing.

00:37:53.665 --> 00:37:56.803
Nobody is bothered about these
useless things.

00:37:56.803 --> 00:38:04.901
So, this is what has to happen and for
that, this is the country where you have

00:38:04.934 --> 00:38:16.784
already, so many blessings of Divinity,
that you can easily get it on this soil

00:38:17.006 --> 00:38:19.226
which is so auspicious.

00:38:21.776 --> 00:38:31.406
I wanted to tell you all this, that
you are searching for the Truth and
yet you are not searching for it.

00:38:32.162 --> 00:38:38.502
Many people, just like that, go to the temple
since they have to, go to the mosque since
they have to, go to the gurudwara since
they have to.

00:38:40.118 --> 00:38:46.418
They don't know why they have to go.
Well, Mother, it's the society, it's
the community, so have to go.

00:38:46.691 --> 00:38:55.398
But what you're getting there is to
be seen. Something has been lost.

00:38:55.398 --> 00:39:02.678
What was lost, as we put it in
Guru Nanak's words, is that,

00:39:02.678 --> 00:39:09.163
"Why should you go for searching in the
forest? The ever-resident, the
ever-detached, is within you."

00:39:09.784 --> 00:39:17.294
Now we'll do all sorts of things.
Then secondly – I've also been to
the Gurudwara many times.

00:39:17.976 --> 00:39:22.946
And used to see that uninterrupted
recitation was going on, people
were memorizing everything.

00:39:23.053 --> 00:39:29.303
Oh, what a great thing He has done
for us! Such a big 'Granth Sahab',
meaning a great treatise.

00:39:29.303 --> 00:39:35.832
Only lines of it are being recited.
That's why Kabir Das ji said, "The
Pandits have become fools after
studying so much."

00:39:36.631 --> 00:39:44.261
What is written inside it? Nanak says,
"Without recognizing your own Self, the
moss of confusion cannot be dispelled."

00:39:45.001 --> 00:39:53.401
Similar is the condition of Hindus,
where it is said, in the Vedas,
in the Puranas, everywhere,

00:39:54.055 --> 00:39:59.745
even Krishna said, 'There is only one
Spirit in everyone,' so how are you
creating castes?

00:40:00.230 --> 00:40:08.860
Why were castes created? You are seeing
its consequences. Still castes exist.

00:40:08.902 --> 00:40:13.132
And casteism has become so strong
that it is hard to understand.

00:40:13.161 --> 00:40:23.635
Just think who was the one who wrote
The Ramayana. Valmiki, a dacoit,
and that too a fisherman.

00:40:23.904 --> 00:40:30.224
After finding him, Ramachandraji
said, "You write my Ramayana."
Couldn't he find anyone else?

00:40:30.639 --> 00:40:35.619
Couldn't find any such pure man?
Caught hold of a dacoit.

00:40:37.194 --> 00:40:44.984
And who wrote the Gita? Who was
the one who wrote the Gita?

00:40:45.684 --> 00:40:56.894
A illegitimate child of a maid. He wrote It.
Tell Me what does this indicate?

00:40:57.834 --> 00:41:03.674
He ate the pre-tasted berries of Shabri.
Why did He do all this?

00:41:03.723 --> 00:41:09.492
Why did He need to do all this,
all this drama? To show,

00:41:10.382 --> 00:41:19.452
that the person who has attained the
essence of saintliness, who has known
Brahma, is the real Brahmin.

00:41:22.671 --> 00:41:30.361
Today who is the one who knows Brahma?
I don't see anyone.

00:41:31.800 --> 00:41:38.030
So where did these castes come from?
Some were made Shudras, some were
made this, some were made that.

00:41:38.030 --> 00:41:48.718
This caste by birth was formed later.
So this irony of Hindu religion is
difficult to see.

00:41:49.136 --> 00:41:52.716
And we're still going with everything
that way.

00:41:52.716 --> 00:42:00.138
And we think this is the greatest act
of religion. There is no dearth of
fake gurus.

00:42:00.138 --> 00:42:04.766
And in every street of your Delhi you'll
find many such gurus and tantriks sitting.

00:42:05.559 --> 00:42:13.469
Many are also surrendered at their feet.
So much has been written about this

00:42:13.725 --> 00:42:18.815
that who is the real Guru? Nanak Sahib
has written an entire chapter on this.

00:42:20.291 --> 00:42:30.231
Who is the real guru? The one who
takes money from you – tell Me?
Does God understand what money is?

00:42:30.787 --> 00:42:40.075
Oh, this is a headache humans have created
for themselves. Does He understand banks,
does He understand money? Does He?

00:42:40.075 --> 00:42:46.525
They are selling Him, selling religion.
They are spreading false rumors.

00:42:46.525 --> 00:42:52.104
"We'll do this and show, we'll do that
and show," and, "Your father's
treasure is buried there."

00:42:52.104 --> 00:42:57.004
And, 'You have such an enmity with
so-and-so,' - all these things to
incite mutual conflict.

00:42:57.447 --> 00:43:01.657
We should also look at their own lives,
how is their own life?

00:43:01.958 --> 00:43:07.018
What is the life of such a man like?
Is there any purity in his life?

00:43:07.018 --> 00:43:13.284
Is there any love, any understanding,
any elevation, any affection? - nothing.

00:43:13.284 --> 00:43:18.299
And they are sitting around posing
as big saints. They collect crores
of rupees.

00:43:18.303 --> 00:43:24.934
This is the wisdom of our Indians these
days. Going wherever everybody is going.

00:43:28.118 --> 00:43:34.698
There were old tales, one of them
was that someone's father said,

00:43:35.550 --> 00:43:40.690
"Look, son, you go where everyone
else goes." Said, "Okay."

00:43:41.076 --> 00:43:46.986
So, standing at the crossroads, he
wondered should follow where
everyone was going.

00:43:47.278 --> 00:43:51.858
They were all heading towards the
crematorium; foolishly he followed them.

00:43:53.681 --> 00:43:58.561
Very few people have the intelligence
that an Indian has.

00:43:59.221 --> 00:44:08.401
Very sorted out, sensible, and intelligent.
Despite having everything,

00:44:08.438 --> 00:44:14.178
in foolishness nobody can - do such
stupid things that cannot understand.

00:44:14.708 --> 00:44:20.098
But the real guru-ghantaals here
— one or two still remain —

00:44:20.208 --> 00:44:24.206
they all went abroad. This is a
good thing, because they are
involved in money.

00:44:24.594 --> 00:44:28.334
We were saved because we are not
that rich.

00:44:28.334 --> 00:44:34.621
This was only God's Grace, otherwise,
as I see people there, they are
rolling on the road.

00:44:35.205 --> 00:44:41.205
This is their condition because
they have destroyed their intelligence
so much. Now there is a gentleman

00:44:41.205 --> 00:44:47.684
he explains that this is how you
conquer and control the minds
of others.

00:44:47.983 --> 00:44:50.813
And he swings a pendulum in his hand.

00:44:50.813 --> 00:44:54.903
They'll have a man stand up and say,
'Look, I can swing this pendulum.'

00:44:54.925 --> 00:45:01.195
Now everybody over there in America,
gape at it. The poor people have never
seen all this kind of stuff.

00:45:01.826 --> 00:45:07.006
Are we born to swing the pendulum?
Is there no other business left?

00:45:07.369 --> 00:45:13.859
The other gentleman says that you
will be able to rise at three feet.
Just tell?

00:45:13.859 --> 00:45:18.856
Oh, the top officials here are his
disciples. What's supposed to be done
with rising at three feet?

00:45:18.856 --> 00:45:22.733
Just now there was so much traffic on
the road, what would have happened had
these three feet gone there?

00:45:23.182 --> 00:45:31.392
As it is there's a jam on the road.
What is this stupid talk? People
believe it and pay many thousand rupees.

00:45:31.446 --> 00:45:34.726
There are different tricks in our
country and different tricks there.

00:45:34.726 --> 00:45:39.301
They have understood that the poor
people there don't know anything.
Whatever you say is right.

00:45:39.301 --> 00:45:43.446
Whatever you tell is fine.
But you people know.

00:45:44.596 --> 00:45:55.956
You know that this is filth, this
is sin, this is immorality. Poor
fellows, they don't know.

00:45:56.241 --> 00:46:06.201
So they have risen so high, and we
still don't think, 'We have to
achieve something.'

00:46:06.201 --> 00:46:11.661
"After all, we came into this world."
Are we here just to waste our lives
like this?"

00:46:14.110 --> 00:46:21.870
Now, all this knowledge of Sahaja
that I am sharing, you will see
is this My knowledge?

00:46:23.141 --> 00:46:27.471
This has been going on in this
country since times immemorial.

00:46:27.666 --> 00:46:37.159
Kabirdasji has said, "Ida, Pingala,
Anhad Nadi, Sukhman Nadi,"

00:46:37.159 --> 00:46:41.889
"Ida, Pingala, Sukhman Nadi,"
it is clearly stated.

00:46:41.889 --> 00:46:48.869
"Shoonya shikhar par anahad baaji re,"
(The unstruck melody resounds at the peak
of the head) but no one understands him?

00:46:48.869 --> 00:46:56.957
I am surprised that in Bihar, where
he did so much work, people call
tobacco, Surati.

00:46:56.957 --> 00:47:04.598
He had called Kundalini as Surati, "Surati
chadhe kamaan." (Kundalini ascends the bow)
Oh my, where has this reached?

00:47:04.598 --> 00:47:10.098
Some people are very clever at
spoiling everything.

00:47:10.098 --> 00:47:12.643
And we are fools and agree with them.

00:47:13.245 --> 00:47:21.515
How great this country is, how great
its greatness is, all this will be
understood when you come into Sahaja.

00:47:21.515 --> 00:47:29.966
When our foreign Sahaja Yogis come here,
then first after alighting from the
airplane

00:47:29.966 --> 00:47:36.678
bow down and kiss this land because
they know what vibrations are.

00:47:37.036 --> 00:47:44.636
They recognize vibrations and know that
these vibrations are flowing from our earth.

00:47:45.223 --> 00:47:50.303
And you people too must have done
no less good deeds that you're
born on this earth.

00:47:52.546 --> 00:47:59.776
This is also a great act of virtue.
It is because of this virtue that
you have come here today.

00:47:59.777 --> 00:48:03.827
Now many people also ask this question,
"So, Mother, what will happen of"
our poverty?"

00:48:04.629 --> 00:48:10.169
That's right. We should first think
from where does poverty come.

00:48:10.789 --> 00:48:21.989
Selfishness, comes from selfishness.
But when a person becomes selfless
and comes into the collective,

00:48:23.865 --> 00:48:32.605
then, this kind of collective form
can completely eliminate poverty.

00:48:33.063 --> 00:48:38.143
Now what can I tell you that diseases
are cured in Sahaja Yoga, you don't
have to pay a single penny.

00:48:38.425 --> 00:48:41.645
All kinds of diseases, including
cancer, have been cured.

00:48:41.645 --> 00:48:47.996
Now, just yesterday, you might have
noticed that there was a woman there
who was blind; she came and told Me,

00:48:47.996 --> 00:48:52.388
"Mother, I have come from so far
to see You, and I cannot even see."

00:48:52.388 --> 00:48:58.049
So I just held a candle in front of her,
and then after a while she says,
"I have begun to see everything."

00:48:58.049 --> 00:49:02.393
I didn't do anything, I didn't do.
Her Kundalini awakened.

00:49:02.393 --> 00:49:07.115
And It shone a light into the optic
lobe here, and she began to see.

00:49:07.690 --> 00:49:14.050
There was a girl who was dumb, couldn't
speak. They brought her to Me.

00:49:14.142 --> 00:49:22.032
Simply whispered Krishna's mantra into
her ear, and from that moment onwards,
she began to speak.

00:49:22.032 --> 00:49:25.325
She called Me "Mother" at that moment
and then she started talking.

00:49:25.641 --> 00:49:29.111
Now this is not a miracle for Me,
no miracle at all.

00:49:30.785 --> 00:49:35.505
Is this a miracle for you?
This is not a miracle.

00:49:35.505 --> 00:49:41.797
See, this Kundalini, when It awakens,
It passes through the six chakras.

00:49:41.797 --> 00:49:48.122
And as it passes through these six
chakras, it illuminates your chakras
completely.

00:49:48.488 --> 00:49:54.418
And It fills it with Its energy.

00:49:54.852 --> 00:49:59.912
It is because of the disturbance in
these chakras that you remain
sick and you suffer.

00:50:00.134 --> 00:50:06.034
And once this Kundalini rises, what
is there to say? Then everything
falls into place.

00:50:06.224 --> 00:50:11.034
All cases are set right, and thousands
of people are cured in this way.

00:50:11.802 --> 00:50:16.522
And if someone comes after doing
something mischievous, it doesn't
work out - don't know why.

00:50:17.714 --> 00:50:24.064
Kundalini knows this very well. She is
your Mother. Everyone's individual Mother.

00:50:24.064 --> 00:50:28.788
And just like a tape recording,
She knows everything about you.

00:50:28.788 --> 00:50:37.934
And if there's humility within you,
then Kundalini rises and does all
the work properly.

00:50:37.934 --> 00:50:41.277
It is true that many people get
cured through Sahaja Yoga.

00:50:41.277 --> 00:50:45.864
This is not a false thing. But don't
come to Sahaja Yoga to get cured.

00:50:45.864 --> 00:50:53.392
Come to get realized, that's good.
Once you are realized, your illnesses
will be cured.

00:50:53.687 --> 00:50:57.647
Many types of diseases were cured.
Those who did not have children,
they had children.

00:50:57.647 --> 00:51:01.909
There are many diseases for which there
is no cure,

00:51:01.909 --> 00:51:05.412
many such diseases are cured by Sahaja Yoga.

00:51:05.463 --> 00:51:11.523
Now look at the farmers here. Many people
have been told that with Sahaja Yoga

00:51:11.523 --> 00:51:17.447
if you cultivate your crops with vibrated
water, you come to Sahaja Yoga

00:51:17.447 --> 00:51:22.147
so that your farming can increase tenfold.
But no one listens.

00:51:22.580 --> 00:51:29.030
People from various agricultural schools
did so much research on it and reported

00:51:29.030 --> 00:51:33.926
'Look, there's been such a research.'
Even a very famous Austrian

00:51:36.775 --> 00:51:44.465
Mr. Hameed, Dr. Hameed, came here,
and he was the first advisor to the UNO.

00:51:44.465 --> 00:51:49.325
He also conducted an experiment and
explained it to everyone.
But I don't know what the matter is.

00:51:49.325 --> 00:51:54.160
It doesn't go into anyone's head. It's
as if someone's head is upside down.

00:51:54.160 --> 00:52:01.078
Well, do farming with this. Farming in this
way, if you see ten fields,

00:52:01.078 --> 00:52:05.952
and if there is a lush green field among
them, then know that it belongs to some
Sahaja Yogi.

00:52:07.483 --> 00:52:14.283
In everything. In animal husbandry.
I've seen that they conducted experiments
and told that

00:52:14.283 --> 00:52:24.629
a cow gives about ten kilograms of milk.
It's quite surprising—our Indian cow.

00:52:24.878 --> 00:52:33.264
And the seeds they use are not just the
kind you buy from a store or something.

00:52:33.264 --> 00:52:40.608
But a very ordinary seed. So much
can grow from that seed. But no
one is willing to listen.

00:52:40.608 --> 00:52:46.261
Now, if you call a newspaper person
in India, then their sight is on

00:52:46.261 --> 00:52:51.176
that there was a carpet laid at your
place, that there was a lamp lit at
your place;

00:52:51.176 --> 00:52:55.740
Is there something beyond that or not?
Don't see anything at all. No one listens

00:52:55.740 --> 00:53:01.090
neither writes anything. Will just write
some stupid things. There's no meaning
in them.

00:53:01.090 --> 00:53:03.547
I have brought such a big thing before you.

00:53:03.547 --> 00:53:06.179
Well, listen to something; No, not
ready to listen.

00:53:07.020 --> 00:53:09.770
Don't know what kind of brain these
people have here.

00:53:09.770 --> 00:53:15.143
On the contrary, if you look in Russia,
that the very old St. Petersburg,

00:53:15.143 --> 00:53:23.106
the oldest, they say, is the Academy
of Science and Arts, they gave Me
such a grand title

00:53:23.106 --> 00:53:27.041
that I was surprised; I said, 'Sir,
I haven't even graduated,

00:53:27.041 --> 00:53:31.253
didn't do anything like science or arts.
So he said,

00:53:31.253 --> 00:53:36.536
"Whatever discoverers there are, the
ones who make discoveries, they never
even go to the university."

00:53:36.536 --> 00:53:40.902
"And here we've only given it to ten
people, and You're one of them,
one is given to Einstein."

00:53:40.970 --> 00:53:43.200
So I said, "Gave it to Einstein,
gave it to Me too."

00:53:43.200 --> 00:53:46.519
"Yes, You have made a greater discovery
than Einstein."

00:53:47.067 --> 00:53:53.267
And out of shame, I, couldn't understand
that I had done anything like that.

00:53:53.267 --> 00:53:59.228
This is our old thing. This is our country's
heritage. This only is our heritage.

00:53:59.234 --> 00:54:05.284
From where to where, so many years ago,
thirteen thousand years ago, Markandeya
wrote in Sanskrit.

00:54:06.716 --> 00:54:14.866
It is certain that earlier, a guru would
take only one disciple. For example, King
Janaka took only one disciple, Nachiketa.

00:54:16.434 --> 00:54:26.204
And this only is the tradition. But
in the twelfth century, Gnyaneshwarji
told his guru, his brother,

00:54:26.204 --> 00:54:31.440
"No, please give Me only this permission
to write about it, please give Me
this much permission."

00:54:31.440 --> 00:54:39.928
And when He wrote the sixth, the sixth
chapter of His Gyaneshwari, in it Kundalini

00:54:39.928 --> 00:54:45.798
is beautifully described, and it is
due to this Kundalini that you
attain enlightenment,

00:54:45.798 --> 00:54:48.530
receive it, this is also clearly written.

00:54:48.530 --> 00:54:53.707
So the Spiritual leaders of that time
who were there said, "This is all
nonsense, this is prohibited."

00:54:53.707 --> 00:54:58.647
"No one should read it, leave it,"
and cut it. Such people are still
there nowadays.

00:54:58.647 --> 00:55:06.381
Some are religious gurus, and others
are all sorts of people who consider
themselves very intelligent.

00:55:07.223 --> 00:55:12.373
And because it's cut off completely,
all those people also leave it.

00:55:12.416 --> 00:55:17.576
But still, a Guru had only one disciple.
The Nathpanthis have done this work.

00:55:17.576 --> 00:55:24.596
Three types of work have been done
here. One was the work of the Vedas,
and from that, Vedanta.

00:55:24.596 --> 00:55:32.935
And another act done was that of
devotion, but the real work was
done by the Nathpanthis

00:55:32.935 --> 00:55:38.932
who have done a lot of work on
the awakening of Kundalini etc.

00:55:39.537 --> 00:55:44.947
Nanak Saheb also knew it, He knew
it very well.

00:55:44.947 --> 00:55:54.464
Namdev was a tailor. In India, the
status of a tailor is not considered
to be of great erudition.

00:55:54.464 --> 00:56:01.808
An ordinary tailor and his maid,
Jana Bai, were also very influential.

00:56:02.175 --> 00:56:06.885
He went to meet a potter, whose
name was Gora Kumbhar.

00:56:06.996 --> 00:56:18.356
That potter was breaking up the
clay with his feet. Seeing him,
Namdev suddenly -

00:56:18.650 --> 00:56:25.080
wonderful people, were wonderful
people. And what did he say,
said in Marathi,

00:56:25.600 --> 00:56:33.090
'Nirguna cha bheti alo sagunachi'.
I came to meet the Formless, but you
are standing in form.

00:56:33.426 --> 00:56:38.982
Who could say such a thing? Who
could say such a great thing
for another person?

00:56:38.982 --> 00:56:43.338
If an Indian meets another and
does not abuse, then only you can
consider yourself happy.

00:56:43.504 --> 00:56:50.514
But what does one saint say when
he sees another saint?

00:56:50.858 --> 00:56:56.968
What is he saying? That You are the
Formless standing in Form.

00:56:57.461 --> 00:57:04.181
Then he went to Punjab. In Punjab
Nanak Sahib recognized him. He
was a very prominent figure.

00:57:04.481 --> 00:57:10.101
He told him that, "Okay, you learn
Punjabi and write in Punjabi."

00:57:10.101 --> 00:57:15.647
And he has written such a big book
in Punjabi, and many of his works
are also included in the Granth Sahib.

00:57:15.647 --> 00:57:22.119
Now this recognition, this understanding,
can only come to saints.

00:57:23.331 --> 00:57:30.341
This sight and this subtle vision
can only come to saints.

00:57:30.341 --> 00:57:37.973
So much change happens in a person after
Sahaj. But I won't say many things because
half the people will get up and leave.

00:57:38.642 --> 00:57:45.332
Meaning this that one gives up alcohol
completely. Everyone said not to drink.

00:57:45.332 --> 00:57:53.335
In Muhammad Sahab's time he said,
"Don't drink alcohol," but cigarettes
didn't exist then.

00:57:53.481 --> 00:57:57.391
So Nanak Sahib came in His place
and said, "Well, don't even smoke
cigarettes."

00:57:58.259 --> 00:58:06.089
But all this is simply been said,
otherwise you go to London and
you'll be shown

00:58:06.089 --> 00:58:11.951
that what a huge pub they have. They
have opened a pub inside their house.
Even the British don't do that.

00:58:11.951 --> 00:58:18.550
They also keep somewhere in the
cupboards, but this is right in front.
There's a pub, a pub.

00:58:20.331 --> 00:58:25.751
This thing that has come that what
they have said, what they have told,

00:58:25.751 --> 00:58:31.068
it has become very difficult for
people to comply.

00:58:31.203 --> 00:58:36.333
Some do it, some do it secretly,
some do it halfway, some do it a lot.

00:58:36.697 --> 00:58:42.557
Because they don't have that strength,
they aren't capable. But in Sahaja Yoga,
you become capable.

00:58:42.561 --> 00:58:47.621
Understand it like this, if I had
a snake in My hand and I am a
very stubborn woman

00:58:47.621 --> 00:58:52.982
and if you say, "You're too
stubborn," then I'll never agree.

00:58:53.585 --> 00:58:58.935
And then, with all the flattery
you say that, "Sir, this snake is
in Your hand, You drop it."

00:58:59.034 --> 00:59:05.774
I'll say, "No, it's a rope." Am
sitting in the dark so it's a rope.
Start insisting on it.

00:59:05.774 --> 00:59:10.906
"This is a rope, this is a rope." In the
end, when the snake bites, only then
will I come to know that it's a snake.

00:59:11.111 --> 00:59:18.551
But when a little light comes in, I
let it go. The thing drops in an instant.

00:59:18.551 --> 00:59:25.860
In this way, the things that have
become ingrained in us, which are
destroying us, are completely removed.

00:59:25.860 --> 00:59:31.120
Man becomes absolutely clean. Yes, there's
one more thing I need to tell you.

00:59:31.153 --> 00:59:38.013
That our famous shehnai player—you know,

00:59:38.013 --> 00:59:43.621
Bismillah Khan Sahib, he once
came to our program.

00:59:44.322 --> 00:59:52.142
So he looked at all the Sahaja Yogis
sitting there and said, "Mother,
You have purified them."

00:59:52.142 --> 00:59:57.073
"These have become so pure." "Yes,"
I said, "Look, they're so pure."

00:59:57.073 --> 01:00:00.375
So I said, "What Khalistan are they creating?"
he asks Me.

01:00:00.375 --> 01:00:03.073
I said, "You go and ask them,
what are you asking Me."

01:00:03.073 --> 01:00:07.594
Whose Khalistan are you creating?
Khalis means pure, clean.

01:00:07.594 --> 01:00:11.987
When you have become pure, this is
what He said, "You become pure."

01:00:11.987 --> 01:00:16.807
And a lot of hard work was done on the
Sikhs. Same is the case with Muslims.

01:00:16.807 --> 01:00:26.923
Muslims were told that a great revolution
called Qiyama had been arranged.

01:00:26.923 --> 01:00:34.062
'When the resurrection comes, your hands
will speak and bear witness against you.'
It has been clearly stated.

01:00:34.642 --> 01:00:43.832
Where did it go? Jesus has said some
wonderful things: "Thou shalt not
have adulterous eyes."

01:00:43.832 --> 01:00:49.192
Just tell, what a great thing it is!
And show Me which of these people
have clean eyes,

01:00:49.192 --> 01:00:56.961
and pure and immaculate? Won't find
any. Reason is - it's not a thing
to be blamed -

01:00:57.013 --> 01:01:01.443
The reason is that,
that within
there is no strength. When that
power comes within

01:01:01.443 --> 01:01:05.994
then man fearlessly sings
'Nirbhay Nirgun'.

01:01:08.167 --> 01:01:16.797
You look around this country, so many
people have done such important work.

01:01:16.811 --> 01:01:27.871
We should not go along with the
attitude these foreigners have
these days

01:01:29.247 --> 01:01:35.967
and neither should we run along
with the enormous progress they
have already made.

01:01:36.290 --> 01:01:46.320
Because go and see what their
condition is. In fact, we need to
protect our spiritual,

01:01:46.991 --> 01:01:54.151
we should see progress in what we
call spirituality. We are very
deserving of it.

01:01:54.216 --> 01:02:00.446
And the whole world will fall at
your feet tomorrow, if you achieve
your spiritual progress.

01:02:00.492 --> 01:02:06.572
But we do not know how big a
source this is within us.

01:02:06.572 --> 01:02:11.610
Now let Me tell you, all of you who have
come, I know you all will get realization
today. There is no doubt about it.

01:02:11.610 --> 01:02:17.860
But if even one-eighth of that number
were in a foreign land, My limbs
would get tired.

01:02:18.855 --> 01:02:26.845
But once they connect, once they are
realized, they stand in such a way
that I don't understand.

01:02:26.845 --> 01:02:32.828
And Indians are such that, "Come on
let's listen to Mataji's speech today,
and tomorrow we'll go there and listen."

01:02:32.862 --> 01:02:38.612
"Then we'll listen to a third person's
speech, then we'll go somewhere to
perform aarti," there's no depth at all.

01:02:38.658 --> 01:02:45.008
And in a country that had and has
such depth, such people have been
in this country

01:02:45.687 --> 01:02:52.277
In that country, for some unknown
reason, man has lost his depth.

01:02:54.988 --> 01:03:01.668
We must understand that all our
questions will be resolved at once.

01:03:01.828 --> 01:03:05.598
And it's also true that whatever dilemmas,
whatever problems are there –

01:03:05.598 --> 01:03:11.664
A gentleman came and was telling Me that,
"Mother, I had so many problems, they
all ran away by themselves."

01:03:11.767 --> 01:03:18.537
"Troubles were in trouble. Now I
have no troubles at all."

01:03:19.379 --> 01:03:22.869
So I said, "How did this happen?"
"This is what I don't understand,
I've come to ask You."

01:03:22.869 --> 01:03:29.057
I said, "Well, don't ask Me." I want
to take you all into this world of bliss.

01:03:29.057 --> 01:03:33.651
I want to take you to a world of such
love where this love is selfless,

01:03:33.651 --> 01:03:38.101
in which there is no depravity of
any kind what is a thing.

01:03:39.158 --> 01:03:45.348
In this Nirvajya means that he
has accepted the power of love.

01:03:45.674 --> 01:03:49.484
This means that there is only the
enjoyment of loving.

01:03:50.719 --> 01:03:58.069
Just look, they said to Me, "Mother,
tell us, what are the things Indians
like, we'll bring those?"

01:03:58.069 --> 01:04:02.782
I said, "Bring a little only," they've
brought it and put it on My head,
and now are saying, "You distribute
it to everyone."

01:04:02.782 --> 01:04:06.835
Now I said, "How can I distribute?
You've brought so much stuff,
who knows what all."

01:04:07.486 --> 01:04:14.856
And have brought them after so much
thought. Said, "Can't find good
needles here," so have brought them.

01:04:14.887 --> 01:04:18.487
"Can't find good scissors here,"
so have brought them.

01:04:18.737 --> 01:04:27.787
Tell Me, with so much thought and love,
and indeed with the kind of, they're
about to have a tour,

01:04:27.787 --> 01:04:34.076
400-500 people, where they live—
they live in such nice houses, they
have cars, they have everything

01:04:34.076 --> 01:04:39.924
- are living very happily. Ask how are
they, "Wow! In great joy. There is
so much joy in India."

01:04:39.924 --> 01:04:44.649
"Well, what's the matter?" They want
the bliss of the Spirit, not the body.

01:04:44.649 --> 01:04:49.360
And Indians are they'll say, "We
want an attached bathroom." These
don't say that.

01:04:49.658 --> 01:04:55.738
Indians are even more amazing. We
built their ashram in Ganpatipule.

01:04:55.738 --> 01:04:59.207
So Indians said that, "We want
Western bathrooms."

01:04:59.207 --> 01:05:02.635
And they said that, "We want Indian
style because they are very clean."

01:05:02.635 --> 01:05:09.154
Now tell, how did this happen?
How did these people change?
How did their views change?

01:05:09.154 --> 01:05:13.063
How did they start understanding
all this? They're all so sweet.

01:05:13.063 --> 01:05:17.106
And the Sahaja Yogis here too are
very lovely. They are very nice.

01:05:17.106 --> 01:05:26.727
Tell Me, an Indian man becomes
completely honest. Have you heard
of it anywhere? Absolutely 100%.

01:05:27.768 --> 01:05:34.008
And they all think it's My money,
"No, no, it's Mother's money,
put it in there."

01:05:35.430 --> 01:05:43.400
We're no less when it comes to stealing
our mother's money. But no, are so honest.
Then, don't tell lies.

01:05:43.719 --> 01:05:50.359
There was a gentleman who said that,
"Mother, I used to think I was a lion
because I used to carry a gun."

01:05:50.359 --> 01:05:53.506
"Now I'm truly a lion. I don't
want a gun, I don't want anything."

01:05:55.801 --> 01:06:01.521
Such people have changed, become so
lovely, because you are truly so lovely.

01:06:02.118 --> 01:06:10.478
Full of love, but had forgotten.
Ultimately, because of lack of
self-knowledge.

01:06:10.478 --> 01:06:16.684
Now gain your knowledge. For your own
knowledge, the knowledge of the Self,
which we call

01:06:16.684 --> 01:06:21.299
Inner Knowledge, and you can know
everything you want about it.

01:06:21.299 --> 01:06:24.496
And you can't pay for this,
understand that first of all.

01:06:25.073 --> 01:06:30.783
Indians don't even understand this.
One day they brought and gave Me
a 25 paise coin.

01:06:30.914 --> 01:06:34.194
I said, "I don't take money."
"Okay, take one rupee."

01:06:35.074 --> 01:06:42.644
They cannot understand that Someone
does something like this for free.

01:06:42.644 --> 01:06:48.798
But how much will you pay for it?
It has no value. It has no value.

01:06:48.798 --> 01:06:56.118
You can't pay for this, and it's not like
if I give a lecture today, it's free,
and then after that money - no money

01:06:57.717 --> 01:07:07.097
at all. You must understand that this
is a game of vibrations, and you cannot
pay money for this game of vibrations.

01:07:07.097 --> 01:07:13.171
And the person who asks you for money
in the name of God, think that, there
can be no greater thief than him.

01:07:13.171 --> 01:07:20.863
He doesn't even fear God. Yes, it's
alright, now they've decorated the
pavilion so beautifully

01:07:20.863 --> 01:07:27.425
you got the expenses for that, that
you can fix up, but you can't pay
for Self-realization.

01:07:27.818 --> 01:07:36.408
What is this thing money? But many
receive the blessings of Goddess Lakshmi.

01:07:36.408 --> 01:07:40.170
Many have said, "Mother, as soon as
we came to Sahaj, we were blessed
by Goddess Lakshmi."

01:07:40.189 --> 01:07:44.399
But this too is an illusion. We
have to go beyond that.

01:07:45.193 --> 01:07:51.233
And going forward, you have to
enjoy the joy of the light of
your Spirit.

01:07:51.519 --> 01:07:55.909
In that bliss, all knowledge stands
before you.

01:07:55.999 --> 01:08:00.659
Because you have everything within
you, you just need to awaken it.

01:08:01.321 --> 01:08:06.221
There is no favor of Mine in that,
no deal is there.

01:08:06.604 --> 01:08:13.314
It's your right which I am giving you;
it is your right only and you must
receive it.

01:08:13.725 --> 01:08:21.175
There's no need to be grateful for
this. But do understand yourself

01:08:21.175 --> 01:08:31.030
that we have found this thing, such a
priceless thing, my Sadguru. I am not
even a guru, I am only a Mother.

01:08:31.239 --> 01:08:35.289
And I didn't even give it to you;
You have received your own thing.

01:08:35.440 --> 01:08:45.050
But don't throw away something so
valuable on the street. Don't
diminish its importance either.

01:08:45.050 --> 01:08:49.453
It's a very important thing. It will
solve every kind of problem.

01:08:49.453 --> 01:08:55.038
This is a Mother saying. One should offer
temptation, right? Tell something or the
other, people get trapped by temptation.

01:08:55.116 --> 01:08:59.696
But the fact is son, you won't
find peace until you get it.

01:08:59.696 --> 01:09:03.376
I tell this to everyone, no one is
at peace without it.

01:09:03.376 --> 01:09:09.177
And the future of this country is that
there are going to be many, many Sahaja
Yogis here. And then see.

01:09:09.177 --> 01:09:13.485
People ask that, "Mother, what is the
future of our country?" I say,
"It is very bright."

01:09:14.204 --> 01:09:22.484
The point is that after attaining
Self-Realization here today, you
should work hard on it.

01:09:22.506 --> 01:09:28.286
Sometimes the connection gets loose,
fix it. There are centers here for that.

01:09:28.286 --> 01:09:32.425
And the second thing you should understand
is that this is a collective system.

01:09:32.535 --> 01:09:36.985
This is a collective arrangement.
It is not something that

01:09:36.985 --> 01:09:39.820
you are now sitting in your home
and doing Sahaja Yoga.

01:09:39.976 --> 01:09:50.896
Have to do that too, but you have to
get along with everyone. Just like a
nail doesn't grow back if it's cut.

01:09:52.093 --> 01:10:03.473
If you become a part of this unified
collective, vibrated Collective Consciousness

01:10:03.851 --> 01:10:13.681
then, no question arises, and you'll be
surprised at the way people will help you.

01:10:13.681 --> 01:10:17.384
If someone here gets some sickness,
they come rushing from Germany.

01:10:17.573 --> 01:10:20.773
Inform anyone, "Look, this is the thing."

01:10:20.773 --> 01:10:24.958
"Yes, he's staying over there, inform
him. Mother, he knows, he'll come."

01:10:25.379 --> 01:10:32.119
The whole world is with you. You
have real kinship in the whole world.

01:10:35.647 --> 01:10:41.437
I will only say that Gnyaneshwar Ji has
said that, "Such a day is about to come."

01:10:41.437 --> 01:10:49.878
"When such people will come and such and
such work will be done," and there is a
very beautiful description in the
Guru Granth Sahib as well.

01:10:50.566 --> 01:10:56.256
It's described everywhere. Just
understand it and believe it

01:10:56.256 --> 01:11:01.891
that this time has come and you are one
of those who can benefit from it.

01:11:02.126 --> 01:11:04.746
May God bless you all!

01:11:21.634 --> 01:11:26.774
Just shift aside, the poor fellow is
not sitting comfortably. You please
make him sit comfortably.

01:11:35.159 --> 01:11:43.140
[A woman cries and mutters something incoherent]

01:11:43.140 --> 01:11:44.397
What's it? Of epilepsy?

01:11:44.397 --> 01:11:46.889
Woman: Yes, epilepsy [UNCLEAR]

01:11:46.895 --> 01:11:52.585
Shri Mataji: Now see, she should understand
that she's brought her daughter and made
her sit in front of everyone.

01:11:52.585 --> 01:11:55.260
Now here people have come for
Self-realization.

01:11:55.141 --> 01:12:01.010
If people here go to our temple,
everyone's illnesses can be cured.

01:12:01.010 --> 01:12:06.850
But she thought, out of her selfishness,
that she should make the child sit in front,
so that everyone would be disturbed.

01:12:06.241 --> 01:12:10.431
Huh? That's wrong. People come
here for self-realization.

01:12:10.623 --> 01:12:13.953
She can be cured, it would hardly
take any time.

01:12:13.953 --> 01:12:20.280
You know, a doctor here has an
M.D. in epilepsy.

01:12:20.280 --> 01:12:22.574
But no one will come at all –
only in front of Mother.

01:12:22.579 --> 01:12:27.659
Only Mother should cure this, Mother
only should do this work. All such
people will come forward.

01:12:28.564 --> 01:12:33.140
Wherever whatever work needs to be
done, must be done. Today it is
about Self-realization.

01:12:33.140 --> 01:12:39.382
Did you understand? Do you understand,
child? Now come, I'll cure you. Okay?
Yes, you're a good girl.

01:12:39.382 --> 01:12:44.458
It'll be done. Let it be now.
Not now, not now. So many people
are sitting just now—okay?

01:12:47.628 --> 01:12:53.168
Our one doctor has done experiments
on this and has received an M.D.

01:12:53.168 --> 01:12:55.845
You shouldn't have sat in front of Me
with your such daughter like that.

01:12:55.845 --> 01:12:59.533
Now My powers are flowing, and
children are harmed by it.

01:12:59.600 --> 01:13:04.760
I think it's better if you take her out.
Will see later. Don't cry, I'll cure her.

01:13:04.978 --> 01:13:08.088
There is nothing to cry about. But
you people won't come to the temple.

01:13:09.791 --> 01:13:17.661
You won't come there and get your
treatment done. There's something
strange about everything.

01:13:17.661 --> 01:13:21.163
Now if you have to wait there for
a while, you get disturbed.

01:13:21.163 --> 01:13:25.038
Well, after all, if you go to the
hospital, you have to wait there as
well, isn't it?

01:13:25.038 --> 01:13:30.787
She'll have another attack; you'd better
take her outside, because My Power
is very active at this time - yes.

01:13:32.103 --> 01:13:35.443
No, no, let her go back, I think.

01:13:35.443 --> 01:13:43.574
Let her go outside a little bit otherwise
she might get another attack. Slowly,
slowly.

01:13:44.592 --> 01:13:50.182
She'll be fine in a moment. We
shouldn't disturb everyone now.

01:13:50.587 --> 01:13:58.277
Yes! Just as she's your daughter, she's
My daughter too; Don't worry. Just pick
her up and take her away.

01:13:58.277 --> 01:14:01.001
For all of you I want to say that
whoever is suffering from any problem,

01:14:01.001 --> 01:14:03.718
you please write a letter and
give it to Me now.

01:14:03.718 --> 01:14:08.364
"We have this problem or this trouble,"
and then you come to the temple.

01:14:08.594 --> 01:14:13.644
We have centers all over the place
here, and everyone can cure you.

01:14:13.644 --> 01:14:18.346
There's nothing like that. So you
all get well. And people do get well.

01:14:18.346 --> 01:14:22.919
But you won't come then how will
it be done? I'm doing something else
here right now, okay?

01:14:24.813 --> 01:14:34.853
Yes, it's okay, sit down. I'm feeling
unwell too, what to do?

01:14:40.603 --> 01:14:46.703
But all these problems can be
solved. I tell you, they all can
be solved.

01:14:46.703 --> 01:14:56.003
You should work a little hard.
Okay, no problem.

01:14:59.942 --> 01:15:06.462
This disease also can go away
very easily, very easily.

01:15:07.039 --> 01:15:12.039
And if her mother practices Sahaja Yoga,
she only can cure her.

01:15:12.420 --> 01:15:17.050
Those who are relations if they
practice Sahaja Yoga, then it will
be of great benefit.

01:15:21.407 --> 01:15:31.682
Come on, now again I say: all those
who want to attain Self-realization
they all should come here.

01:15:31.682 --> 01:15:36.174
And those who don't want to take it,
please go away, then it's a good thing.

01:15:37.314 --> 01:15:43.014
And it's just a matter of ten minutes;
For Indians, it takes no time at all.

01:15:43.014 --> 01:15:46.182
But if everyone could please sit
down, it would be a great favor.

01:15:46.329 --> 01:15:56.579
Because I told you that the Earth
that is, the greatest country on it
is My India.

01:15:56.579 --> 01:16:03.062
And you're sitting in this, just
tell - you believe it.

01:16:24.827 --> 01:16:30.307
Now everyone has to raise their hands
towards Me like this, lifting them.

01:16:32.197 --> 01:16:38.597
Not too much, simply just keep your
hands, as much as you can tolerate.

01:16:38.597 --> 01:16:40.849
Not too much like this, keep
your hands like this.

01:16:42.360 --> 01:16:48.590
Now, I told you that these fingers
which are, five, six, and seven,
are your seven chakras.

01:16:49.306 --> 01:16:57.186
And these seven chakras, here on the left
and the right, they have to be awakened.

01:16:57.200 --> 01:17:07.220
Through these, the Kundalini will be
invoked. Through these - it is
absolutely scientific.

01:17:07.308 --> 01:17:12.608
And doctors also believe that these
are the endings of the sympathetic.
They do believe.

01:17:13.554 --> 01:17:17.714
But they don't know its utility, what
to do further. Straight like this.

01:17:20.271 --> 01:17:26.471
And it would be good to take off your
glasses, because this is also good
for the eyes.

01:17:33.790 --> 01:17:39.980
Now you close the eyes and don't
open them until I tell you to.

01:17:43.829 --> 01:17:51.319
Don't chant any mantras, no thoughts to
be suppressed, no need to do anything;
Kundalini does everything on its own.

01:17:51.319 --> 01:17:58.392
Thus sit comfortably, relax completely,
and have complete confidence in yourself,

01:17:58.392 --> 01:18:07.449
that today only you will attain
Self-realization, today. With humility.

01:18:11.380 --> 01:18:18.800
You, this is a pure desire and ask
that, "Mother, please give us Self-
Realization," in your mind.

01:18:19.470 --> 01:18:26.750
Today itself this is going to happen,
because your will must be manifested.

01:18:26.750 --> 01:18:32.003
You should say that, "We want that
we get Self-realization."

01:18:37.669 --> 01:18:39.649
Don't open your eyes now.

01:18:39.979 --> 01:18:44.919
Please close your eyes and don't open
them till I tell you.

01:18:45.603 --> 01:18:48.063
You can remove your spectacles.

01:18:55.350 --> 01:19:00.440
[Shri Mataji blows into the mic]

01:19:01.020 --> 01:19:04.757
[Shri Mataji blows into the mic]

01:19:05.748 --> 01:19:07.648
