01:19:27.261 --> 01:19:29.979
[Shri Mataji blows into the mic]

01:19:29.979 --> 01:19:33.463
[Shri Mataji blows into the mic]

01:19:33.463 --> 01:19:35.916
[Shri Mataji blows into the mic]

01:19:35.916 --> 01:19:38.785
[Shri Mataji blows into the mic]

01:19:40.034 --> 01:19:44.044
[Shri Mataji blows into the mic]

01:19:45.264 --> 01:19:49.164
Please open your eyes slowly.

01:19:51.567 --> 01:20:00.297
Now, put your left hand towards Me, like
this and bend your head and see through

01:20:00.297 --> 01:20:07.031
your fontanel area, bone area, if you are
getting a breeze, a cool maybe hot.

01:20:07.031 --> 01:20:16.299
Put your left hand towards Me and
bend your head please. Bend your head
and see with your left hand

01:20:16.603 --> 01:20:24.303
whether some cool or warm breeze
is coming out of your palate.

01:20:24.303 --> 01:20:31.192
Palate is, that is a soft part of the
head in childhood, which is called
the palate.

01:20:31.192 --> 01:20:39.571
You look at it, whether a cool breeze is
coming from there? It could be warm too.

01:20:39.788 --> 01:20:45.996
If you're feeling warm, say this
within yourself, "Mother, I forgive
everyone altogether."

01:20:45.996 --> 01:20:52.379
Very easy to say this. Just say,
"Mother, I forgive everyone at once,"
then the heat will go away.

01:20:56.666 --> 01:21:04.246
Bend your head, bend your head;
and not on your head, but above
what is called suspended.

01:21:04.246 --> 01:21:11.977
Stay above, slightly away from it.
Now, place your right hand towards
Me and bend your head again.

01:21:12.723 --> 01:21:20.183
And now see with the left hand,
some get very close and some
very far away.

01:21:20.183 --> 01:21:28.299
For some very subtle, and some very strong,
this is how the wind blows—you see this,
cool or hot breeze.

01:21:29.611 --> 01:21:34.041
Bend your head and don't be doubtful
in any way.

01:21:40.771 --> 01:21:44.351
Please put your left hand towards Me.

01:21:44.351 --> 01:21:48.818
Again bend your head and right hand
towards Me.

01:21:48.818 --> 01:21:53.354
Please see with your right hand, if
there's a cool or a hot breeze coming.

01:21:53.354 --> 01:21:58.934
If it is hot, then you have to say in your
heart, "Mother, I forgive everyone."

01:22:09.023 --> 01:22:15.616
Don't doubt yourself and don't think
this, "I'm a great sinner," and forget
all these things just now.

01:22:16.146 --> 01:22:23.925
Because this Supreme Consciousness that
is, is an ocean of forgiveness.

01:22:23.925 --> 01:22:28.114
You can't make any mistake that
doesn't get dissolved in it.

01:22:34.115 --> 01:22:40.155
It is an ocean of mercy, an ocean of
knowledge, but greatest of all,
It is an ocean of forgiveness.

01:22:44.969 --> 01:22:51.479
Now raise both hands and look
towards the sky.

01:22:53.913 --> 01:23:03.383
And ask a question, "Mother, is this the
Supreme Consciousness?" Today you are
experiencing for the first time.

01:23:03.552 --> 01:23:10.862
Please ask the question, "Mother, is this
the Cool Breeze of the Holy Ghost?"

01:23:10.862 --> 01:23:15.277
Or, "Mother, is this the Divine Power of
Love?"

01:23:15.277 --> 01:23:21.239
For the first time you are feeling it. Just
lift your head upwards and see for
yourself.

01:23:21.253 --> 01:23:27.173
You'll feel on your hands or fingers.
Now put down your heads.

01:23:28.591 --> 01:23:36.361
Again please put your hands towards
Me. Don't think.

01:23:36.912 --> 01:23:43.202
You can do it; first state of nirvichar
samadhi, of thoughtless awareness.

01:23:43.202 --> 01:23:45.621
Don't think, just don't think.

01:23:53.966 --> 01:24:01.086
Now, whoever is feeling the cool breeze
or the hot breeze in their hands,

01:24:01.667 --> 01:24:09.587
or in the fingers, or cool or hot air
is coming from the palate

01:24:09.612 --> 01:24:14.672
All those who are feeling cool breeze
or hot breeze on their hands,

01:24:14.672 --> 01:24:18.915
on the finger-tips or through their
fontanel bone area

01:24:19.273 --> 01:24:23.183
all such people raise both your
hands above.

01:24:23.183 --> 01:24:26.970
Please raise both your hands - all
such people who are feeling.

01:24:27.210 --> 01:24:36.240
See, just see, just see so many saints and
sages. My loving greetings to all of you!

01:24:36.240 --> 01:24:42.887
You have become a saint, have become
a sage, the whole of Delhi - Oh my God!

01:24:42.887 --> 01:24:51.837
[Applause]

01:24:55.941 --> 01:25:04.961
Now just be in enjoyment, be in joy.
And come to the Collective.

01:25:04.961 --> 01:25:11.533
We have centers everywhere here.
I want to see all the seeds that
have been sown,

01:25:11.533 --> 01:25:16.786
and the saplings that have now sprouted
from them may become large trees.

01:25:17.196 --> 01:25:26.456
All the seeds which were sown, have
now become beautiful - what child?

01:25:27.210 --> 01:25:31.130
Sit down, sit down, sit down;
Nothing happened?

01:25:32.040 --> 01:25:36.920
Okay, sit down, sit down, will happen,
will happen, patience, patience.

01:25:42.938 --> 01:25:56.238
What are you saying? You're cured?
What is there now, what more is needed;
Just get well, everyone.

01:26:02.055 --> 01:26:11.575
Now, it's like this, some people get
cured instantly, they get cured right
during the program, I don't know what
it is.

01:26:11.575 --> 01:26:18.401
And some people need to come a little.
Whatever it is, if you want to get
better, what's the harm in that?

01:26:18.401 --> 01:26:24.912
May have to come back once or twice more;
but many people are healed suddenly just
like that. There's no doubt about it.

01:26:26.264 --> 01:26:38.954
Seeker: Mataji [UNCLEAR]

01:26:38.954 --> 01:26:44.480
(UNCLEAR)

01:26:44.480 --> 01:26:49.510
Sahaja Yogi: Gets some sort of a
tingling sensation in the feet and
hands, but he can come in the centre.

01:26:50.511 --> 01:26:57.111
Shri Mataji: At least come to the center.
No, no, there's no problem. Please
come to the center.

01:26:57.111 --> 01:27:01.726
And your liver is damaged. They will
tell you what the treatment is.

01:27:01.726 --> 01:27:07.710
And that will alleviate all your troubles,
Okay.
Seeker: (UNCLEAR)

01:27:07.710 --> 01:27:13.037
Shri Mataji: But since you haven't
even made any effort, what's the
point in complaining about it?

01:27:13.037 --> 01:27:18.611
Make some effort first, and if it
doesn't work out, then it's okay.
Come and see at least.

01:27:18.611 --> 01:27:19.782
Seeker: I will definitely do that.

01:27:19.782 --> 01:27:23.222
Shri Mataji: How many people here
can raise their hands and say

01:27:23.222 --> 01:27:26.489
that they didn't benefit from
Sahaja Yoga, tell Me? Indians.

01:27:28.779 --> 01:27:35.268
Has been very beneficial. Look, so
many people are sitting here. Then
why wouldn't it be for you?

01:27:37.727 --> 01:27:40.397
Sahaja Yogi: All brothers are being informed

01:27:40.397 --> 01:27:49.190
Shri Mataji: I'm just saying that
all those who have, who - what do
you say to benefit - hmm?

01:27:49.235 --> 01:27:53.755
Haan, have got some sort of a benefit
out of Sahaja Yoga,

01:27:53.755 --> 01:27:58.594
those who have got some benefit out
of Sahaja Yoga, you put up your hands.

01:28:00.323 --> 01:28:07.373
Wow, wow! Now look. Now when so many
people have benefited, then now what,
what more this thing do you want?

01:28:11.328 --> 01:28:17.058
Sahaja Yogi: We have many centers
all over Delhi and a chart is
made for them.

01:28:17.058 --> 01:28:19.158
It's a flyer, you will get it.

01:28:19.648 --> 01:28:26.238
In the follow-up program, which we have
kept for this program, in Nizamuddin,

01:28:26.238 --> 01:28:33.953
you people come to the Indian Scout
Ground at 11 o'clock. Who
(UNCLEAR) hasn't felt yet

01:28:33.953 --> 01:28:39.131
we will work on you and you may
feel it there.

01:28:39.131 --> 01:28:46.156
We have a main center behind the
Qutub Bhavan, where our (UNCLEAR)
address is listed.

01:28:46.156 --> 01:28:49.879
You, there's a program every
Saturday, come there.

01:28:49.879 --> 01:28:56.561
We run a centre for newcomers on
Wednesdays in Safdarjung Enclave,
come there.

01:28:56.561 --> 01:29:02.147
If any brother has any problem,
which is a personal problem,
we all resolve it there.

01:29:02.147 --> 01:29:05.400
If there's something we can't cure,

01:29:05.400 --> 01:29:09.112
then we pray to the Shri Mataji
and She helps you.

01:29:09.112 --> 01:29:16.591
My only request to you is that you all
please come to the center, and I am
confident that you will all enjoy it.

01:29:20.613 --> 01:29:26.803
Tomorrow at 11 am at Indian Scout Ground,
opposite Nizamuddin Police Station.

01:29:28.711 --> 01:29:36.301
And on the 8th, it's at the Ashram in
Safdarjung Enclave; you can find the
address here, at 6:30 in the evening.

01:29:38.061 --> 01:29:44.651
Shri Mataji: Sing a song or two,
then I'll leave. Today the ...

01:29:50.793 --> 01:29:57.733
All these foreigners are singing, see,
you can't imagine. They even sing very
well in Marathi.

01:29:57.733 --> 01:30:00.268
You will not be able to recognize
who is singing.

01:30:00.731 --> 01:30:07.641
Otherwise, teaching them even a
single word of Hindi would have
been a very difficult task.

01:30:16.498 --> 01:30:21.658
Sit down and listen to this song, you'll
enjoy it. Sit down. Listen to a song.

01:30:21.658 --> 01:30:29.022
It will feel good. Now you will
enjoy the song.

01:30:47.934 --> 01:30:56.864
Just sit down, he is telling you to
come and they will tell you everything.

01:30:57.763 --> 01:31:02.173
Now, please come tomorrow. What date?
They've invited you tomorrow. Come
tomorrow at 11 o'clock.

01:31:02.173 --> 01:31:08.698
And after that they have centres all
over Delhi. There are many centres.
They'll tell you everything.

01:31:08.698 --> 01:31:12.465
In a month you'll become a guru of
yourself and of everyone else.

01:31:16.421 --> 01:31:25.501
Listen, no, no, no, no [MARATHI]
What are you doing?

01:31:25.937 --> 01:31:29.127
Not this song. This is for Maharashtra
desha.

01:31:29.127 --> 01:31:33.512
We are not sitting in Maharashtra
desha, this time alright? Sing some
other song.

01:31:33.512 --> 01:31:39.391
What are you doing? Tell an appropriate
song. That gentleman from Noida, that
boy, he was singing well.

01:31:42.039 --> 01:31:49.029
[MARATHI]

01:32:00.059 --> 01:32:03.489
[MARATHI] Saat janam [MARATHI]

01:32:06.090 --> 01:32:10.450
This song, this song was composed
by these people, and they also
composed the tune.

01:32:18.357 --> 01:32:27.347
