01:39:30.862 --> 01:39:34.846
Sit for a minute, sit for a minute.

01:39:53.030 --> 01:39:56.002
These people want to sing one more song.

01:39:56.002 --> 01:40:07.282
Sit down. Everyone is happy. This
song is sung during Guru Puja;
what should one ask from the Guru?

01:40:34.741 --> 01:40:45.961
